{"tid":2433157,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特幣會一飛衝天，衝上月球，衝上火星，最終成為世界性的貨幣","createTime":"2021-03-04T19:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T19:10:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dd7efbf0f1eef856bcd2e0a6cbb37ffb79a0852b","tid":2433157,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T19:07:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/加密貨幣交易所kraken執行長-比特幣未來十年料可升至100萬美元-134452505.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80kraken%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E9%95%B7-%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%99%E5%8F%AF%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3100%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-134452505.html&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUk%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=fe01aca5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/加密貨幣交易所kraken執行長-比特幣未來十年料可升至100萬美元-134452505.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【彭博】-- 作為加密貨幣交易所Kraken的執行長，Jesse Powell勢必看好比特幣。然而，他的預測甚至超乎了比特幣最忠實擁躉的想象。<br />\n<br />\n接受彭博電視採訪時，Powell表示，比特幣可能在未來十年觸及100萬美元，還稱支持者認為比特幣最終會取代所有的主要法定貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n「我們只能猜測，但如果用美元衡量，那麼一定會認為比特幣沒有極限，」他說。「真正的信奉者會告訴你，比特幣會一飛衝天，衝上月球，衝上火星，最終成為世界性的貨幣。」"},{"pid":"0c6b9e3655e6a6cefb946754bf2745dbb982efa3","tid":2433157,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T19:10:42.000Z","msg":"乜撚野特幣<br />\ntesla coins? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}